        "TileImage": "$($repository 18207e15-3ef6-41a3-a342-3c6e638222b6).Image",
        "Description": "This time you are send to Berlin. Your job again will be to eliminate some of criminals hiding in there.\r\rFirstly, take out both &quot;Mishoo&quot; dealer and his supplier from bikers. They are the last important people in here.\r\rNext on the list is &quot;Florida Man&quot;, known for selling drugs in... Fruits. Of course without telling his customers. Interesting guy.\r\rLast two are Club owner, involved in bikers interest and laundering money in there and also Agent Montgomery who is main power in agency.\r\rGood luck",
